Package ca.corefacility.gview.layout.feature Description

Provides for implementations to construct particular "shapes" for a feature. Each instance of a shape is constructed from an implementation of a particular FeatureShapeRealizer, which uses SlotPath/SequencePath to draw out shapes along the sequence.
